Wauthier Braine - Noucelles is finished (OSM is good on this one). It is possible to remove the track in OSM between Niderand and Wauthier Braine ? As encoded now, you can think that there is something ongoing so you might pass but there is nothing at all so you have to take the regular roads. Imagine if you are with kids thinking there is a way between Wauthier Braine and Noucelles to discover when you arrive that you have to use the unsafe roads with your kids ? Not ideal. It&#39;s best to just don&#39;t put anything on the map until is it complete.
